8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], and Vanta [ https://substack.c=
om/redirect/b5a118be-adcc-41be-a875-69d09dd725f8?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8=
J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]
Packy here. You read a lot (often here) about AI doing the things humans do=
n=E2=80=99t want to do so that we can spend our time doing the things we do=
=2E But what does that mean in practice?=20
